      Nautica Voyage Eau De Toilette, Cologne and Fragrance For Men, Fresh, Romantic, Fruity Scent Woody, Aquatic Notes of Apple, Water Lotus, Cedarwood, and Musk Ideal Day Wear, Long Lasting 6.7Fl oz

      Important information

      Safety Information

      For external use only.

      Ingredients

      Alcohol Denat., Aqua/Water, Parfum/Fragrance, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Benzyl Salicylate, Butylphenyl Methylpropional, Benzophenone-3, Limonene, Hydroxyisohexyl 3-Cyclohexene Carboxaldehyde, Linalool, Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Geraniol, Coumarin, Propylene Glycol, Citral, Isoeugenol, Methyl 2-Octynoate, BHT, Benzyl Alcohol, Acrylates/Octylacrylamide Copolymer, Disodium EDTA, Hydrolyzed Jojoba Esters, Ext. D&C Violet 2 (CI 60730), FD&C Blue 1 (CI 42090), FD&C Yellow 5 (CI 19140), D&C Red 33 (CI 17200), FD&C Green 3 (CI 42053).

      Directions

      Apply to pulse points (wrists, neck, and behind the ears). A little goes a long way. Suitable for both day and night wear.

      How customer reviews and ratings work

      Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

      To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we dont use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

        The Nautica Voyage Eau De Toilette for Men has proven to be a standout fragrance, offering a captivating blend of fresh, romantic, and fruity notes that effortlessly combine to create a scent profile that exudes sophistication.

        **Fragrance Composition (5/5):**
        The fragrance opens with invigorating top notes, featuring a harmonious fusion of fresh and fruity accords. The subtle sweetness of apple is complemented by the aquatic essence of water lotus, creating an uplifting and energetic introduction. The heart notes then unfold, revealing a delicate yet robust interplay of scents, leading to a warm and woody finish dominated by cedar.

        **Longevity (4/5):**
        The longevity of Nautica Voyage is commendable for an Eau De Toilette, offering a lasting impression without becoming overwhelming. The transition from the initial burst of freshness to the deeper, more complex base notes ensures that the fragrance remains relevant throughout the day.

        **Versatility (4/5):**
        The versatility of this fragrance is noteworthy. Its balanced composition allows it to seamlessly transition from day to evening wear. Whether in a professional setting, a casual outing, or a romantic evening, Nautica Voyage adapts well, adding a touch of refinement to any occasion.

        **Packaging (4/5):**
        The packaging of the Nautica Voyage Eau De Toilette aligns with its nautical inspiration, featuring a sleek, blue-toned bottle reminiscent of the open sea. The design is both modern and timeless, reflecting the essence of the fragrance it houses.

        **Compliment Factor (5/5):**
        One of the standout features of this fragrance is its ability to garner compliments. The fresh and romantic notes seem to resonate well with those in proximity, making it an excellent choice for individuals seeking a fragrance that leaves a positive and lasting impression.

        **Overall Impression (4.5/5):**
        In conclusion, the Nautica Voyage Eau De Toilette for Men lives up to its promise of delivering a nice fragrance that balances freshness, romance, and woody sophistication.         **Final Thoughts:**
        For individuals seeking a fragrance that captures the essence of a fresh sea breeze with a touch of romance and sophistication, Nautica Voyage stands out as a commendable choice. Its well-balanced and captivating composition makes it a fragrance that can be enjoyed on a daily basis and for special occasions alike.
